title: Instant (YC S22) Is Hiring a Founding TypeScript Engineer
summary: Instant, a Y Combinator S22 startup, is currently seeking a founding TypeScript Engineer to join their team. The company is focused on developing an AI-powered database that utilizes TypeScript for its backend. Instant is hosting an AI Startup School in San Francisco on June 16-17, and those interested in learning more or applying to the position can find more information on their website.
